Dear Hiring Team,

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the *Full-Stack Engineer* role with *Openmart*. I bring over three years of engineering experience across AI-native systems and full-stack product delivery, along with a Master of Science in Computer Science from Pace University.

